      • AdjMatGraph

        public AdjMatGraph()

      • AdjMatGraph

        public AdjMatGraph(java.lang.String inFileName)
        Second constructor take as input a file with an extension .tgf and read it as follows: The file has two parts separated by a sharp symbol (#). The first part lists all the vertices, one per line. A vertex is described by two items: a vertex number and a String label. The second part lists all the arcs, as a pair of vertex numbers separated by space.
